def capital_indexes(string):
    # List to store the indices of capital letters
    index_list = []
    
    # Iterate over each character in the string
    for i in range(len(string)):
        # If the character is a capital letter, add its index to the list
        if string[i].isupper():
            index_list.append(i)
            
    return index_list
